34 "Discrimination" includes any unfair treatment based on a person's presumed or
35 assumed race, color, religion, national origin, ancestry, sex, sexual orientation, gender
36 identity, age as it relates to employment, disability, veteran status, or familial status as it
37 relates to housing, regardless of whether the presumption or assumption as to such
